com.saptarshidebnath.lib.processrunner.exception

Class ProcessException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.saptarshidebnath.lib.processrunner.exception.ProcessException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ProcessException
extends Exception
    Blanket custom Exception. The class need to be used by the RunnerFactory class and all public facing methods for this Runner library. The Developer should be able to get the cause from the Throwable.getCause() detailing exactly what triggered the exception.
